  "detailed_description": "<h1>Greek DLC: A Taste of Greece</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2733690/extras/d63ef5bf3be575d6f1fe0ce552bdf3a9.avif?t=1766342927\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2733690/extras_big/d63ef5bf3be575d6f1fe0ce552bdf3a9.webp?t=1766342927 width=1560 height=248 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Check out Grub Truck's first DLC: A Taste of Greece, featuring tasty greek cuisine menu items, a hand-crafted location, lots of new Build Mode objects/items, a new truck and new managers!</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Cook, Plan & Decorate as you run your very own food truck business. Serve Customers, Buy & Sell Trucks, Strategise Menus & Complete Quests as you become the next budding Grub Truck entrepreneur!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2733690/extras/92f80f72414ab104553d55e2eb7de9ec.poster.avif?t=1766342927\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2733690/extras/92f80f72414ab104553d55e2eb7de9ec.webm?t=1766342927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2733690/extras/92f80f72414ab104553d55e2eb7de9ec.mp4?t=1766342927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cook & Serve!</h2>Cook from a variety of dishes (from Tacos and Burgers to Onion Rings and Side Salads) and serve them fast to keep your hungry customers happy!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2733690/extras/d1683fd6f8b8154d6373aa4d881c803e.poster.avif?t=1766342927\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2733690/extras/d1683fd6f8b8154d6373aa4d881c803e.webm?t=1766342927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2733690/extras/d1683fd6f8b8154d6373aa4d881c803e.mp4?t=1766342927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Buy/Sell Trucks & Hire Managers!</h2>Invest in new trucks and hire managers to enhance your daily business operations, or sell your older models to free up extra capital.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2733690/extras/bda3fd80543576a3f62e24c153b5d3ae.poster.avif?t=1766342927\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2733690/extras/bda3fd80543576a3f62e24c153b5d3ae.webm?t=1766342927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2733690/extras/bda3fd80543576a3f62e24c153b5d3ae.mp4?t=1766342927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Design & Decorate your Truck</h2>Buy new appliances, sell old ones and decorate your truck to attract more potential customers.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2733690/extras/6dced1b312c47e003ced9cb7f560ae1d.poster.avif?t=1766342927\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2733690/extras/6dced1b312c47e003ced9cb7f560ae1d.webm?t=1766342927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2733690/extras/6dced1b312c47e003ced9cb7f560ae1d.mp4?t=1766342927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Complete Player Quests</h2>Choose from a selection of playable characters as you attempt to achieve their quests whilst navigating their diverse quirks.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Wishlist Now!</h2>Ready to Turn Your Passion into Profit? Wishlist the game or play the free demo - available now!",
  "about_the_game": "Cook, Plan & Decorate as you run your very own food truck business. Serve Customers, Buy & Sell Trucks, Strategise Menus & Complete Quests as you become the next budding Grub Truck entrepreneur!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2733690/extras/92f80f72414ab104553d55e2eb7de9ec.poster.avif?t=1766342927\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2733690/extras/92f80f72414ab104553d55e2eb7de9ec.webm?t=1766342927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2733690/extras/92f80f72414ab104553d55e2eb7de9ec.mp4?t=1766342927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cook & Serve!</h2>Cook from a variety of dishes (from Tacos and Burgers to Onion Rings and Side Salads) and serve them fast to keep your hungry customers happy!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2733690/extras/d1683fd6f8b8154d6373aa4d881c803e.poster.avif?t=1766342927\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2733690/extras/d1683fd6f8b8154d6373aa4d881c803e.webm?t=1766342927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2733690/extras/d1683fd6f8b8154d6373aa4d881c803e.mp4?t=1766342927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Buy/Sell Trucks & Hire Managers!</h2>Invest in new trucks and hire managers to enhance your daily business operations, or sell your older models to free up extra capital.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_